OL,3,CMajor Devon creamery expansion to
OL,4,Ccreate 100 jobs
OL,6,FAround 100 jobs are set to be created
OL,7,Fat a Devon creamery following a
OL,8,Fmultimillion-pound investment to
OL,9,Fexpand production at the site.
OL,11,FDairy giant Arla has announced it is
OL,12,Finvesting more than #179m in the UK as
OL,13,Fpart of its plans to become a "major
OL,14,FUK exporter of mozzarella."
OL,16,FThe co-operative is currently the
OL,17,Fthird-biggest supplier of mozzarella
OL,18,Fin the world.
