OL,6,FTaw Valley Creamery, in North Devon,
OL,7,Fis to be updated with state-of-the-art
OL,8,Ftechnology, enabling the site to
OL,9,Fproduce mozzarella within the next
OL,10,Fthree years, as part of the plans.
OL,12,FPeter Giortz-Carlsen, COO of Arla
OL,13,FFoods Europe, said the investment will
OL,14,Fenable the company "to stay among the
OL,15,Fleaders within mozzarella."
