OL,3,CMajor Devon creamery expansion to
OL,4,Ccreate 100 jobs
OL,6,F"Our mozzarella business has seen
OL,7,Fdouble-digit growth over the past five
OL,8,Fyears and we have strong relationships
OL,9,Fwith key customers, particularly in
OL,10,Fglobal food service, and it's from
OL,11,Fthat very solid starting point we are
OL,12,Fannouncing the investment today," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FMaria Chacon-Cubo, from Taw Valley
OL,16,FCreamery, said the expansion will
OL,17,Fdouble the workforce bringing dozens
OL,18,Fof jobs to Devon.
