OL,3,CMajor Devon creamery expansion to
OL,4,Ccreate 100 jobs
OL,6,F"We already have a high-skilled and
OL,7,Fmotivated workforce, so being able to
OL,8,Fpush that and grow those teams is
OL,9,Fgoing to be incredible," she said.
OL,11,FShe added: "It is also allowing us to
OL,12,Fuse more of the milk pool in this
OL,13,Farea. We are in the heart of one of
OL,14,Fthe biggest producers of milk, and
OL,15,Fbeing able to use it locally really
OL,16,Fbenefits farmers."
OL,18,FArla is now seeking planning
OL,19,Fpermission to enable the business to
OL,20,Fmake changes to the creamery.
